{"tid":495771,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(#Metoo) 弘揚女權正氣，焚燒邪書名單","createTime":"2017-12-11T04:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T11:00:57.000Z","uid":54337,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b775bf2fcc240288fd804a981b43aec57b97e94d","tid":495771,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:23:52.000Z","msg":"古往今來，實在有太多書籍，鼓吹男女不平等，甚至煽動侵犯女性權益，我每次閱讀相關邪書妖書，都敢怒不敢言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我素來G持男女平等及捍衛女性權益。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我見到荷里活的 #Metoo浪潮，我就知道，我也要為女性權利站起來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下是一系列邪書，公然主張侵害女性，簡直豈有此理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位#Metoo的fan屎，齊齊站起來，齊齊燒書吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女性萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男女平等萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbacc8f5db9de7424e3366726b2e3628a3ed289","tid":495771,"uid":54337,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:24:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒書No.1：論語</span></span></strong><br />\n(原因)<br />\n孔仲尼在論語陽貨，曾經曰：唯女子與小人為難養也，此句說話明顯是歧視婦女，種下男女不平等的千年禍根。孔家店公然踐踏女性尊嚴，何其可惡！<br />\n<br />\n(總結)<br />\n廢話唔使講，燒書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒書No.2：西遊記</span></span></strong><br />\n(原因)<br />\n<br />\n1. 唐三藏、孫悟空、豬悟能、沙悟淨、白龍馬，師徒五人，無一個係女性，明顯係性別歧視，人人duck耳豬芝。<br />\n<br />\n2. 其中有一幕，孫悟空三打白骨精。孫悟空是男，白骨精是女。孫悟空三次公然打女人，明顯是男性野蠻的沙文主義向女性權益粗暴的擴張和侵犯，天地不容。<br />\n<br />\n3. 盤絲洞蜘蛛精全部是女人。作者將女性妖魔化，嚴重破壞女性權益及尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n(總結)<br />\n廢話唔好多講，燒書。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燒書No.3：三國演義</span></span></strong><br />\n(原因)<br />\n<br />\n1. 其中一幕，劉安殺妻，獻妻肉待客。作者將女人貶為男人附屬物品，嚴重歧視女性。<br />\n<br />\n2. 王允欲殺董卓，於是獻上貂蟬。貂蟬是女人，有自主的權益和尊嚴，但王允將貂蟬物化，將之淪為自己的附屬財產，可以隨便轉手獻給他人。這一幕嚴重歧視女性及公然鼓吹物化女性的一鼓歪風 (an unhealthy wind)，人人duck耳豬芝。<br />\n<br />\n(總結)<br />\n廢話唔好多講，燒書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒書No.4：水滸傳</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(原因)<br />\n1. 梁山泊一百零八位豪傑，只有一位係女性，該位女性仲要有個綽號，叫母夜叉。母夜叉，是貶意。作者開宗明義貶低女人地位，令人氣憤。<br />\n<br />\n2. 故事中，武松是男人，潘金蓮是女人。武松殺潘金蓮，是公然吹鼓男性赤裸裸的沙文主義向女人人身安全、地位、權益的不合理踐踏，令人憤慨難平。<br />\n<br />\n3. 作者配偶有季氏及申氏。此三妻四妾的行為，是男尊女卑的封建邪惡思想，嚴重打擊男女平等的天地正氣(healthy wind between sky and land)<br />\n<br />\n(總結)<br />\n廢話唔多講，燒書。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒書No.5：詩經</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(原因)<br />\n有女懷春，吉士誘之。<br />\n白茅純束，有女如玉。<br />\n舒而脫脫兮，無感我帨兮。<br />\n<br />\n此詩講述男女在野外性交，詩中女性沒有批准 (Without Consen)，就被男性強行性侵，作者明顯鼓吹男性對女人作性侵犯，及歧視女性的軀體自主及性愛自主，簡直天理不容，人神共憤。<br />\n<br />\n(總結)<br />\n廢...... 燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒書No.6：聖經</span></span></strong><br />\n(原因)<br />\n<br />\n新約聖經啟示錄明言，世界末日之前，有出現一隻巴比倫女淫獸。聖經公然將女性貶為一隻邪惡淫賤的禽獸妖怪，簡單不知所謂，無法無天，令人怒髮沖冠。<br />\n<br />\n(總結)<br />\n<br />\n廢......燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">待續 ...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"68f6c39a47ad631359518493fa01caf9b43666e5","tid":495771,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:29:55.000Z","msg":"其實係唔係覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講咁多 即刻駁嘴"},{"pid":"ffeed047b3426dc763870a4696f40b900e401046","tid":495771,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"女權力量是否不足，或過大，值得商榷<br />\n<br />\n不過，基於宗教、迷信、反科學傳統、反科學文學來反女權，就真係需要把它們燒左去佢。基於科學、心理學或社會科學，反女權又好，撐女權又好，都要keep。"},{"pid":"29f0c682b2a9c58d2d33b1dc49b6c4f18d1adfe6","tid":495771,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:02:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒書No.7 ：哈姆雷特 </span></span></strong><br />\n(原因)<br />\n<br />\n莎士比亞罪大惡極，公然表示：&ldquo;弱者，你的名字是女人! &rdquo; (Frailty, thy name is woman!)。&nbsp;<br />\n莎士比亞把女性標籤為軟弱無能的弱者，令人怒火燒胸。<br />\n<br />\n(總結)<br />\n廢話唔使多講，燒書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒書No.8：奧賽羅</span></span></strong><br />\n(原因)<br />\n<br />\n黑人男主角奧賽羅，在床上揑死其白人妻子達狄蒙娜。莎士比亞罪大滔天，又再一次公然鼓吹男性對女性施加暴力及傷害女性身體的一鼓歪風 (a drum of unhealthy wind)，簡直不知所謂，天地難容。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(總結)<br />\n廢 ........ 燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a542cf6dc6ac49aee49a96bb6008c631cc270d0","tid":495771,"uid":86893,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://enjoy.eastday.com/e/20080328/images/01236570.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fenjoy.eastday.com%2Fe%2F20080328%2Fimages%2F01236570.jpg&h=68688c8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bf4f1a09bdc0c60c81392dabdf454712053bc3b","tid":495771,"uid":17368,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"樓主識咁多邪書，燒"},{"pid":"f698f09a145533b3eabc10dae7a4238107cd586d","tid":495771,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/160040_f5ed5c1aab94af19afb3373755e57ea8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F160040_f5ed5c1aab94af19afb3373755e57ea8.gif&h=ba0b45f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n捍衛女權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男女平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n替天行道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n弘揚天地正氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf99ba2201ce0cebf88a617394a73535180053f","tid":495771,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/162242_7de11a39cebc82bdfcd9d9bc1b149b26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F162242_7de11a39cebc82bdfcd9d9bc1b149b26.jpg&h=de0ba7d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#metoo 嘅fan屎，齊齊燒書啦喂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b776997fe3e759e553b6361a1e058a26dca291ca","tid":495771,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:25:14.000Z","msg":"講得太好，尤其梵蒂肛竟然仲禁止女性做教皇同紅衫馬騮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea9b7bf4a3e7097ee0ad545563b2e1c21be65eb","tid":495771,"uid":2864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506134d8f143acc64d495a2b121e63602fde8540","tid":495771,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"撚女權撚得合理啲好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地針對緊現代，古代係人都知男女地位唔平等，父權社會，樓主比返啲現代例子啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bfaecf498916771ff10bc9a59ef322c2268709b","tid":495771,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撚女權撚得合理啲好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地針對緊現代，古代係人都知男女地位唔平等，父權社會，樓主比返啲現代例子啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宗教和迷信風俗，繼續影響現代社會<br />\n<br />\n香港班女權撚，一樣用返中國傳統對女性有利的風俗，來撚班男人。例如要送一堆金器比女家，要俾幾萬蚊禮金女家。<br />\n<br />\n基督教會，又話男人係頭，結果班港女就要求男人要好醒好smart，做超人咁。"},{"pid":"2617332553a5052dcd4d62331f49eb534002099d","tid":495771,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:56:58.000Z","msg":"樓主竟然冇提《古蘭經》<br />\n<br />\n滴汗。"},{"pid":"c5ad973d145cae61f49084c3b2a24f378fff299a","tid":495771,"uid":156321,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/190046_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F190046_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=04f8a76d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}